  "texts": [
    "Information Communication and Media (ICM) is a rapidly growing field that integrates society, culture, and technology (Fuchs 2009).",
    "Amid the hype surrounding artificial intelligence (Newlands 2021), professionals in ICM fields such as telecommunications, journalism, entertainment, marketing, social media and information technology now face the question of whether they can trust the technologies they help to create.",
    "Although human-robot communication is a critical topic in academic research over the last decade (Feher and Katona 2021), research on the challenges and future visions of ICM systems are sporadic or under-represented in academic publications and strategic AI documents.",
    "This is why it is particularly relevant to investigate the visions of ICM professionals.",
    "The key research question is how ICM fields are changing due to AI technology and what the key consequences are expected to be."
  ],
